This project is no longer active. See https://github.com/bpoore/pbm-react for the active Pinball Map app.

=========

Android Application for http://pinballmap.com

CHANGELOG
=========

version 2.1.3
-reset user-reported conditions
-display conditions inline in location details
-new UI for selecting regions
-numerous fixes for crashes

version 2.1.2
-email screens for adding new regions and contacting regional admins
-search by type
-minor UI updates
-bug fixes from crash reports

version 2.1.1
-top level zone menu item
-bug fixes from crash reports

version 2.1
-use PBM api to pull data
-numerous UI/UX updates
-bug fixes from crash reports

version 2.01
-sort machine names ignoring leading "The"
-email all region admins with location suggestions
-list all available machines in Add Machine page
-Google Analytics tracking
-commas for high scores
-new icon assets

version 2.00
-target the 4.4 sdk instead of the 2.2 one
-move to google maps android v2
-remove deprecated methods

version 1.08
-fix for Android > 2.1 closest locations crash
-better threading

version 1.07
-crash report fixes from android marketplace submissions
-reintroduced motd and location suggestions
-less aggressive httpconnection attempts...because older phones were getting stalled from this

version 1.06
-crash report fixes from android marketplace submissions

version 1.05
-crash report fixes from android marketplace submissions
-allow location suggestions directly from the phone

version 1.04
-crash report fixes from android marketplace submissions
-new icon

version 1.03
-crash report fixes from android marketplace submissions

version 1.02
-bug fixes from android marketplace submissions
-added milwaukee image
-stopped creating mock locations to pass around
-caching of address information

